I know that I fall in the minority of Domino's customers but I really loved the old pizza! I remember eating it all the time back in 2008 while I was playing Spongebob Squarepants Operation Krabby Patty on my computer or watching cartoons on TV. Those were good times! ;(

You know what? I'm so done with you Domino's! Pizza Hut is now my go to pizza place. They have better pizza, better breadsticks, better everything pretty much! :)
